Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: UN unanimous on Iran-Iraq
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440fjg
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 26 Jul 1987
Russians back out of unanimous United Nations vote over Iran-Iraq conflict. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.